      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SHINBONER SMOKEY (1) is having his first try over the longer journey. Comes here after a last start 5th and beaten 11 lengths (18.22) at this track. Looks well placed and should feature. CHIEF WIGGUM (2) had to overcome a collision with another runner and could manage only a distant sixth (30.45) in a Grade 6 over 509m at this track. Better than last start and can bounce back. FRANTIC PHYLLIS (8) turned in a plain effort last time when fifth at Cannington over 275m behind Wild Mood (16.53) in a Grade 5/6. Placed at her previous run. Some good form is emerging from her last run. Likely to be thereabouts. PINGELLY PRINCE (7) can find the frame without surprising.",
